snippet.title: My Undead Neighbors - Mr. Clumsy vs Zombies
snippet.description: In one day Mr. Clumsywoke up in a house full of zombies and traps. Now he has to find the key and exit in each of the ten levels. But the hero is not so simple, he has a  super look that can not only kill the monster but also activate mechanisms that it is impossible to get yourself
